#{56}":[66,66],"##Highlights#{57}":[67,67],"##Highlights#{58}":[68,68],"##Highlights#{59}":[69,69],"##Highlights#{60}":[70,70],"##Highlights#{61}":[71,71],"##Highlights#{62}":[72,72],"##Highlights#{63}":[73,73],"##Highlights#{64}":[74,74],"##Highlights#{65}":[75,75],"##Highlights#{66}":[76,76],"##Highlights#{67}":[77,78],"##Looking for the right Church. Not to hold grudges against other church.":[79,81],"##Looking for the right Church. Not to hold grudges against other church.#{1}":[80,81],"##Marriage is amazing because it is the closest two people can get, but they can’t get all the way to that place of absolute knowing. [[Marriage; Relationships]]":[82,85],"##Marriage is amazing because it is the closest two people can get, but they can’t get all the way to that place of absolute knowing. [[Marriage; Relationships]]#{1}":[83,85],"##Our soul need other people to be healthy - lonelyness is part of the fall.":[86,90],"##Our soul need other people to be healthy - lonelyness is part of the fall.#{1}":[87,87],"##Our soul need other people to be healthy - lonelyness is part of the fall.#{2}":[88,88],"##Our soul need other people to be healthy - lonelyness is part of the fall.#{3}":[89,90],"##“If we are not willing to wake up in the morning and die to ourselves, perhaps we should ask ourselves whether or not we are really following Jesus.” ([Location 2285](https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B007D6I3VW&location=2285)) [[Faith]] [[Faith_reflect]]":[91,94],"##“If we are not willing to wake up in the morning and die to ourselves, perhaps we should ask ourselves whether or not we are really following Jesus.” ([Location 2285](https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B007D6I3VW&location=2285)) [[Faith]] [[Faith_reflect]]#{1}":[92,92],"##“If we are not willing to wake up in the morning and die to ourselves, perhaps we should ask ourselves whether or not we are really following Jesus.” ([Location 2285](https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B007D6I3VW&location=2285)) [[Faith]] [[Faith_reflect]]#{2}":[93,94],"##I used love like money, but love doesn’t work like money. It is not a commodity. When we barter with it, we all lose.":[95,100],"##I used love like money, but love doesn’t work like money. It is not a commodity. When we barter with it, we all lose.#{1}":[96,96],"##I used love like money, but love doesn’t work like money. It is not a commodity. When we barter with it, we all lose.#{2}":[97,97],"##I used love like money, but love doesn’t work like money. It is not a commodity. When we barter with it, we all lose.#{3}":[98,98],"##I used love like money, but love doesn’t work like money. It is not a commodity. When we barter with it, we all lose.#{4}":[99,100],"##[[Nobody will listen to you unless they sense that you like them.]]":[101,104],"##[[Nobody will listen to you unless they sense that you like them.]]#{1}":[102,102],"##[[Nobody will listen to you unless they sense that you like them.]]#{2}":[103,104],"##When the church does not love its enemies, it fuels their rage.":[105,105],"##I loved the fact that it wasn’t my responsibility to change somebody, that it was God’s, that my part was just to communicate love and approval. [[Faith]]":[106,109],"##I loved the fact that it wasn’t my responsibility to change somebody, that it was God’s, that my part was just to communicate love and approval. [[Faith]]#{1}":[107,107],"##I loved the fact that it wasn’t my responsibility to change somebody, that it was God’s, that my part was just to communicate love and approval. [[Faith]]#{2}":[108,109],"##Inner strength, comes from receiving love as much as it comes from giving it.":[110,112],"##Inner strength, comes from receiving love as much as it comes from giving it.#{1}":[111,112]},"outlinks":[{"title":"rw-book-cover","target":"https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/I/51CdQ6pFQmL._SL200_.jpg","line":3,"embedded":true},{"title":"Donald Miller","target":"Donald Miller","line":6},{"title":"Location 233","target":"h